**Summary:** This documentation describes the Amplitude to CleverTap event streaming destination integration that forwards real-time event data and user properties from Amplitude to CleverTap's retention cloud platform, requiring CleverTap Account ID, Passcode, and Region configuration with support for user creation/updates and selective event filtering.

